This playbook contains four roles
1. check_uptime- It will check and display uptime of the apache service
2. copy_logfile- It will copy log file(access log and error log) from server to local machine at log folder
3. restart_service- It will restart apache service
4. send_mail- It will send email with attahcment of log files

Procedure to run playbook-
1. Clone git repository on your machine
2. change node ip address and public key as per your machine names
3. run command ansible-playbook site.yml
